headline: CSX Corp. Announces Date for First Quarter Earnings Release and Earnings Call
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., March 19, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- CSX Corp. (NASDAQ: CSX) will release first quarter financial and operating results after the market close on Wednesday, April 16, 2025. This will be followed by a conference call and live webcast hosted by the company’s management team at 4:30 p.m. Eastern Time.
